data.description: Plenty of room to spread out! This home is a rare find on the St. Charles Mesa! With a little TLC, sweat equity and your finishing touches, it is a great place to call home! Large kitchen with plenty of counter and storage space along with double ovens make this a perfect place for entertaining! There is lots of room to store all of your toys! Easy access to I-25 and beautiful views of the city lights! Contact us today for your private showing.
